{"id": "art-362", "label": "Art. 362", "title": "Art. 362: Măsurile preventive în cursul judecăţii", "slug": "art-362", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_706664112\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1791\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_706664112\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 362:\nM&#259;surile preventive în cursul judec&#259;&#355;ii </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1714679982\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1790\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1714679982\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În tot cursul judec&#259;&#355;ii, pân&#259; la\npronun&#355;area hot&#259;rârii, instan&#355;a se pronun&#355;&#259;, la cerere\nsau din oficiu, cu privire la luarea, înlocuirea, revocarea sau încetarea de\ndrept a m&#259;surilor preventive.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_215422386\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1789\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_215422386\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În cauzele în care fa&#355;&#259; de inculpat s-a dispus\no m&#259;sur&#259; preventiv&#259;, instan&#355;a este datoare s&#259;\nverifice, în tot cursul judec&#259;&#355;ii, pân&#259; la pronun&#355;area\nhot&#259;rârii, în &#351;edin&#355;&#259; public&#259;, legalitatea &#351;i\ntemeinicia m&#259;surii preventive, procedând potrivit dispozi&#355;iilor art.\n208.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}